Okay bro — I think I see it now, and it’s not what we thought.

You changed fdir1 per wheel and got:

    Left/Right inverted ❌

    J still struggles 2 sec

    Then moves forward instead of pure strafe ❌

That tells me something huge:
fdir1 is probably NOT being interpreted the way we think in gz-sim.

I checked your file and saw this:

<collision>
